column5: Well next Saturday  I will be starting to replace my front porch on the house. Already got a quote on the lumber and will be picking it up Saturday early AM. Now I have a project to do.  By the time I am finished I will not want to see another porch for I don't know how long.. Then on to FISHING
Geez Kelvin, PORCH kinda sounds like PERCH !!!!!!!!    Paul
Pretty Close don't you think Paul...
